These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
Birthday: january, october, may, march
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and Birthday:october##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Birthday:january##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. Birthday:october is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of Birthday:may##1
6. Birthday:october is somewhere to the left of Birthday:january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Birthday      | may  | october | march        | january |

