.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
Cigar: bolivar, game, ritmeester, pall-mall
Sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is somewhere between Sport:skateboarding and Cigar:ritmeester##7
2. Cigar:pall-mall is somewhere to the left of Cigar:bolivar##5
3. Cigar:pall-mall is somewhere to the right of Sport:volleyball##5
4. Cigar:game is on the left of Cigar:pall-mall##1
5. Sport:volleyball is between Sport:skateboarding and Sport:rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Cigar     | ritmeester | game       | pall-mall         | bolivar     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

