.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
Movie-Genre: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
Hobby: camping, skydiving, board-games, traveling
1. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the right of Hobby:traveling##1
2. Hobby:traveling is somewhere between Hobby:skydiving and Hobby:camping##7
3. Hobby:board-games is on the left of Movie-Genre:scientific##1
4. Hobby:camping is somewhere between Hobby:traveling and Movie-Genre:crime##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Hobby   | board-games | camping  | traveling   | skydiving |

