.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Hobby: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
City: miami, berlin, edinburgh, boston
1. City:boston is on the far left or far right##3
2. Hobby:collecting is somewhere between City:berlin and Hobby:writing##7
3. Hobby:woodworking == City:boston##1
4. City:edinburgh is on the left of City:boston##1
5. Hobby:traveling is on the left of City:miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| City   | berlin      | miami   | edinburgh | boston  |

