3. Pet:snake is on the left of Pet:dog##1
4. Food:pomegranate is somewhere to the right of Pet:goldfish##5
5. Pet:goldfish is on the left or right of Food:cauliflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | ferret    | goldfish | snake     | dog |
| Food   | cauliflower | asparagus  | pomegranate | eggplant |

 